gw.plugin.numbergenerator

Interface INumberGenerator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface INumberGenerator
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    The INumberGenerator plugin provides methods for generating human-readable identifying numbers for various entities. These methods will be called before new instances of these entities are committed.
